sequenceDiagram
  participant U as User
  participant C as CLI/API
  participant O as Orchestrator
  participant P as Provider
  participant S as Storage

  U->>C: ask/embed/decide
  C->>O: normalized request
  O->>P: generate/complete
  P-->>O: output
  O->>S: persist session/history/index
  O-->>C: response + metadata
  C-->>U: final output
